The '''''Collège des médecins du Québec''''', or '''Quebec College of Physicians''', is a [[Professional association|professional organization]] responsible for setting educational standards and policing its members at the provincial level in [[Quebec]]. Its mission is to promote quality [[Health care|medical care]] in order to protect the public.<ref>{{cite web|title=Collège des médecins du Québec - Our Organization|url=http://www.cmq.org/en/etudiantsresidents/profil/commun/AProposOrdre/Organisation.aspx|website=Collège des médecins du Québec|publisher=Collège des médecins du Québec|accessdate=23 February 2015|date=2009}}</ref>

